name: Penny Pax
description:
A Request

Penny Pax is an American pornographic actress and model. She is the winner of multiple awards most including the AVN Awards in 2014 for the Best Actress.

Trained on 1.5 Base model but examples are from Analog Madness

Skews NSFW but it's easy to make SFW images. It also skews towards big eyes(As Ms. Pax's are a fan favorite feature). It can veer into caricature from picture to picture. Please adjust prompts for perfect eyes or the like.

***Note this is an experimental TI. I used Blip 2 captions without much editing to them to see if it improves the normal process.

Any feedback/suggestions/recommendations particularly on this model as it is a change in the process would be greatly appreciated
